Variable.Label: Âge

Variable.Formula:
isnull($DATENAIS$) then $TRAGE$ 
else if not(isnull($DATENAIS$)) and $AGE$ < 15 then "1"
else if not(isnull($DATENAIS$)) and $AGE$ > 14 and $AGE$ < 18 then "2"
else if not(isnull($DATENAIS$)) and $AGE$ > 17 and $AGE$ < 25 then "3"
else if not(isnull($DATENAIS$)) and $AGE$ > 24 and $AGE$ < 40 then "4"
else if not(isnull($DATENAIS$)) and $AGE$ > 39 and $AGE$ < 60 then "5"
else if isnull($DATENAIS$) and isnull($TRAGE$) then null
else "6"
Variable.Label: Tranches d'âges calculées (TRAGE6)

if $SITUAEU$ = "1" then (
    if $STCPUB$ = "2" or $STCPUB$ = "3" or $STCPUB$ ="4" then (

else if $SITUAEU$ = "5" then "7"
